              <span id="reviewTextContainer3572592706" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7483041765809002201">As twisted and convoluted this plot was, I didn’t hate it. I struggled for awhile but the story came together in the end . I like his writing style and even though there was so much repetition, I still thought it was written well . It probably could have been 150 pages less . </span>

          </span>
