    <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/list/3075.John_Irving">Books by John Irving</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
